    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "在王子等人与莱昂尼多和谢斯的联军\\n正面交锋的几天前，\\n法尔艾斯曾出现在王宫地下深处的监狱中。\\n探求真理的第二王子试图解放\\n被视为阿尔贝里亚王室禁忌的存在。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "尤蒂尔率领的\\n新阿尔贝里亚军\\n和莱昂尼多&谢斯率领的\\n狄涅尔军正面交战的\\n几天前……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "自从上次我来之后，\\n有什么变化吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "不、不，并没有……\\n别说是变化了……\\n连一点响动都没有。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "那个……法尔艾斯大人……\\n那个房间里到底有什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你不必知道。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "属下明白……\\n但、但是，再这样下去，\\n感觉快要疯了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "一想到在这种昏暗的\\n王宫地下深处一直守着\\n不知道是什么的东西……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你无论如何都想知道吗？\\n那么……今天就招待你\\n一起进入那个房间吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "真、真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "嗯。因为我对人类的好奇心\\n抱有特别的敬意。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "呼……\\n这就是最后一道门……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "还是那么小心谨慎……\\n没想到那位哥哥还挺胆小呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "因为我们得到了\\n“要再三小心”的吩咐……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "那么，属下就开门了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "来，尽情地看吧。\\n看看阿尔贝里亚王室\\n最大的禁忌……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "！？\\n这是……\\n在……沉睡吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "确切地说是被强力的魔法\\n剥夺了意识的状态。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "原来如此，用这个束缚之力……\\n但是，多么不祥……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这个东西叫作封魔具。\\n也是全大陆最厉害的术士们\\n倾力打造出来的特制品。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "好了……差不多到时间了。\\n我们走吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "是！遵命！\\n那就回去吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "呼……法尔艾斯大人……\\n非常感谢您。\\n这件事我决不外传……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你满意了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "可以再多观察一会儿哦。\\n直到你尽兴为止。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "哈、哈啊……\\n可是，刚才法尔艾斯大人\\n说“到时间了”……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "啊，不是的。\\n我刚才的话不是对你，\\n而是对“他”说的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "“差不多到时间了”……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "这、这是……\\n法尔艾斯大人，这到底是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "呃……糟、糟了！\\n得尽快通知王宫！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "没那个必要。\\n他已经被解放了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "警卫",
            "context": "怎、怎么会……\\n来人！快来人！\\n哇啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "与得到满足的好奇心一同消逝。\\n真是充实的生命最后时刻呢。\\n好了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "阿尔贝里亚王室最大的禁忌——\\n缺乏智慧的人这样称呼他。\\n然而，我的看法却不同。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "他是“最大的可能性”。\\n力量本身并不可怕，\\n应该掌握其原理并驾驭它……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "让你久等了。\\n醒来的感觉如何……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "并不坏……\\n法尔艾斯……哥哥……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}